# ğŸ³ PHASE 5 â€” Dockerize Frontend (Multi-Stage Build)

### 9ï¸âƒ£ Frontend `Dockerfile`

ğŸ“ `frontend/Dockerfile`

```dockerfile
# Build stage
FROM node:18-alpine as build
WORKDIR /app
COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm install
COPY . .
RUN npm run build

# Production stage
FROM nginx:alpine
COPY --from=build /app/dist /usr/share/nginx/html
```

âœ” What you learned:

* Production build
* Multi-stage Docker build

